Hi Moriah, I just wanted to say that I really love your videos and have watched every single one, or at least the majority. I love all of your ideas and I really wanted to suggest some future video ideas. I understand that you may have other ideas so it will take a long time to follow through with the ideas (only if you like them, if course!).

The first one is not actually an idea but I would love it if you did more thrift store makeovers but I know that it can be hard to find something that you want to paint.

Another idea was that you could re-paint squishies that you hate, some mentioned in this video but I imagion that you have something like that in mind.

You could make a huge squishy, like life size and completely paint it and decorate it.

More DIYs for room decor, I loved your unicorn ones made a while back and I thought you could do more as they were great!

And my last idea, I don't know how this would work but edible squishies that actually work as squishies that are slow risind and soft. Kind of like a squishy bake over but not quite.

I really like your videos and I cannot wait to watch your next ones!!!
Thank you so much for an amazing year xx

My whole bedroom is now dedicated to rainbow and it has rainbow wall spot stickers on one of my walls. Thanks to you, you pretty much made me who I am today and I hope you don't stop you Channel ever (obviously one day you will)
Xx
